markdown_template_child-docs.Rmd (main file)
--> used to illustrate how child documents can be used in knitr
--> can be used as template to create html/docx/letx/... reports
    with knitr and pandoc

my_R_function.R (R function to draw the plots)

figure/
--> directory containing the generated figures

child-batchrem.Rmd, child-datagen.Rmd, child-dataplot.Rmd
--> child documents contributing to final report

markdown_template_child-docs.md
--> markdown file generated by knitr

markdown_template_child-docs.html
--> final html generated with knitr (generated by compiling 
    markdown_template_child-docs.Rmd)

report-via-pandoc.docx, report-via-pandoc.html
--> final report in .docx and .html generated with pandoc based
    on markdown_template_child-docs.md

